### Create feedback
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/feedbacks
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Slug: acme
X-Correlation-Id: demo-create-feedback-001

{
  "source": "MANUAL",
  "title": "Premium purchase is not activated",
  "content": "Customer says they purchased premium but the account still shows free plan.",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "metadata": {
    "platform": "android",
    "appVersion": "1.0.0",
    "country": "TR"
  }
}

### List feedbacks
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/feedbacks
X-Tenant-Slug: acme
X-Correlation-Id: demo-list-feedbacks-001

### List feedbacks by status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/feedbacks?status=NEW
X-Tenant-Slug: acme
X-Correlation-Id: demo-list-feedbacks-status-001

### List feedbacks by priority
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/feedbacks?priority=HIGH
X-Tenant-Slug: acme
X-Correlation-Id: demo-list-feedbacks-priority-001

### Missing tenant header
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/feedbacks
X-Correlation-Id: demo-missing-tenant-header-001

### Wrong tenant slug
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/feedbacks
X-Tenant-Slug: unknown-company
X-Correlation-Id: demo-wrong-tenant-001

### List feedbacks paginated
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/feedbacks?page=0&size=10
X-Tenant-Slug: acme
X-Correlation-Id: demo-list-feedbacks-page-001

